<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:16:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国防部长称加拿大军舰通过台湾海峡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canadian-warship-transited-through-taiwan-strait-defense-minister-says-2024-07-31/</link><description>加拿大国防部长表示，一艘加拿大军舰最近通过台湾海峡，重申了加拿大对“自由、开放和包容”的印太地区的承诺。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 16:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canadian-warship-transited-through-taiwan-strait-defense-minister-says-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与美国海军在南海举行联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-navy-hold-joint-exercise-south-china-sea-2024-07-31/</link><description>菲律宾武装部队表示，菲律宾和美国海军周三在南海举行了联合海上演习。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:49:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-navy-hold-joint-exercise-south-china-sea-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>BMX-阿根廷和中国队在自由泳比赛中夺得金牌，但热门球队却惨遭淘汰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/cycling/bmx-chinas-deng-takes-gold-womens-freestyle-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三，在巴黎炎热的阳光下，首次参加奥运会的阿根廷和中国选手在 BMX 自由式决赛中夺得金牌，一连串戏剧性的撞车事故将卫冕奖牌得主击倒。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:14:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/cycling/bmx-chinas-deng-takes-gold-womens-freestyle-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国预计未来五年城镇化率接近70%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-expects-urbanisation-rate-near-70-next-five-years-2024-07-31/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国国务院周三表示，预计未来五年常住人口城镇化率将提高到接近70%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:48:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-expects-urbanisation-rate-near-70-next-five-years-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球——中国新科王王惨遭淘汰；年轻的勒布伦占上风</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-newly-crowned-wang-suffers-shock-elimination-by-swedish-2024-07-31/</link><description>庆祝夺得乒乓球混双金牌不到24小时后，中国选手王楚钦在单打比赛中惨遭瑞典选手特鲁斯·莫加德出局，莫加德在周三的比赛中表现出色，晋级16强。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:42:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-newly-crowned-wang-suffers-shock-elimination-by-swedish-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>优步与比亚迪合作将电动汽车引入全球网约车平台</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/uber-byd-partner-bring-evs-ride-hailing-platform-globally-2024-07-31/</link><description>过去两年，电动汽车的高价格和借贷成本的增加成为了电动汽车采用的障碍。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/uber-byd-partner-bring-evs-ride-hailing-platform-globally-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国指责美国议员麦戈文干涉并实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-accuses-us-lawmaker-mcgovern-interference-imposes-sanctions-2024-07-31/</link><description>中国外交部表示，中国以干涉中国内政为由对美国议员吉姆·麦戈文实施制裁，冻结其资产并禁止他在中国进行交易。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:43:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-accuses-us-lawmaker-mcgovern-interference-imposes-sanctions-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>GE医疗保健因中国问题下调2024年收入增长预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/ge-healthcare-cuts-2024-organic-sales-growth-forecast-shares-fall-2024-07-31/</link><description>GE医疗集团周三下调了今年的收入增长预期，原因是中国医疗保健行业因反腐败运动而陷入冻结，拖累了其成像设备和其他医疗设备的销售，导致其股价下跌10%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:36:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/ge-healthcare-cuts-2024-organic-sales-growth-forecast-shares-fall-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国选手全、陈夺得女子双人10米跳台跳水金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-quan-chen-claim-gold-womens-synchronised-10m-platform-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三，中国选手全红婵/陈钰曦在女子双人10米跳台比赛中夺得金牌，延续了中国跳水队的连胜纪录。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:23:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-quan-chen-claim-gold-womens-synchronised-10m-platform-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院推迟中国开发商世茂的清算申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/hong-kong-court-adjourns-china-developer-shimaos-liquidation-petition-2024-07-31/</link><description>陷入困境的中国房地产开发商世茂集团周三表示，香港法院已将该公司的清算听证会推迟至8月12日，从而使其有更多时间与债权人就修订后的重组方案进行合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:18:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/hong-kong-court-adjourns-china-developer-shimaos-liquidation-petition-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>德国指责中国对制图机构进行2021年网络攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-summons-chinese-ambassador-over-2021-cyberattack-cartography-agency-2024-07-31/</link><description>德国周三指责中国幕后策划了 2021 年针对联邦制图机构的网络攻击，以从事间谍活动，并召见北京大使前往柏林提出申诉。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:55:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-summons-chinese-ambassador-over-2021-cyberattack-cartography-agency-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>ASML 希望能在下一轮中美芯片大战中幸免于难</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-shares-up-hopes-it-will-be-spared-next-round-us-china-chip-fight-2024-07-31/</link><description>最大的电脑芯片制造设备制造商阿斯麦 (ASML) 股价周三大幅上涨，此前路透社报道称，该公司可能会免受美国正在考虑的对华出口新限制的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-shares-up-hopes-it-will-be-spared-next-round-us-china-chip-fight-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国在西方审查下修改无人机出口管制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-adjust-drone-export-control-measures-sept-1-2024-07-31/</link><description>中国将从9月1日起修改无人机出口管制，包括将高精度测量设备列入管制清单，并调整部分无人机零部件标准。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:10:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-adjust-drone-export-control-measures-sept-1-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国铁木摊贩抗议处罚政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-temu-vendors-protest-over-penalty-policy-2024-07-31/</link><description>一名参与抗议的商家告诉路透社，Temu 上的数百名中国卖家抗议该公司施加的难以忍受的高额罚款，这是与低成本竞争对手 Shein 进行激烈价格竞争的新迹象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:42:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-temu-vendors-protest-over-penalty-policy-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>索尔维向欧洲供应稀土金属以减少对中国的依赖</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/solvay-aims-produce-30-eus-needs-critical-components-evs-wind-turbines-2024-07-31/</link><description>比利时化工集团索尔维表示，该公司计划通过其位于法国的翻新工厂向欧洲供应稀土金属，用于电动汽车和风力涡轮机中使用的永磁体，以帮助欧洲大陆减少对中国的依赖。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 07:42:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/solvay-aims-produce-30-eus-needs-critical-components-evs-wind-turbines-2024-07-31/</guid></item></channel></rss>